node.text:
#SpeedoUSAAmbassador @michaelandjavi #makewaves by sharing their love of water, with each other. #TeamSpeedo knows how to make waves in and out of the pool. 

How about you? Tell us how you're making waves this summer and tag us #TeamSpeedo @SpeedoUSA for a chance to be featured.

📸 @ivananhe
